Container Interaction Commands

docker exec -it <container_id> bash -Opens terminal inside a running container.
docker logs <container_id>-Shows container output logs.
docker inspect <container_id>- Displays detailed configuration in JSON format.
docker stats-Shows live CPU, memory usage of containers.
docker top <container_id>Displays running processes inside container.


